ja|Shk\u00ebndija 79]]\n| [[Tetovo]]\n| [[Ecolog Arena|Gradski stadion Tetovo]]\n| 15,000\n|-\n| [[FK Sileks|Sileks]]\n| [[Kratovo, North Macedonia|Kratovo]]\n| [[Gradski stadion Kratovo|Stadion Sileks]]\n| 5,000\n|-\n| [[FK Sloga Jugomagnat|Sloga Jugomagnat]]\n| [[Skopje]]\n| [[\u010cair Stadium (North Macedonia)|Chair Stadium]]\n| 6,000\n|-\n| [[FK Vardar|Vardar]]\n| [[Skopje]]\n| Gradski stadion Skopje\n| 18,104\n|}\n\n==League table==\n<onlyinclude>{{#invoke:Sports table|main|style=WDL\n|source=[http://macedonianfootball.com/1-mfl-2004-05-final-standings/ MacedonianFootball.com], [http://www.rsssf.com/tablesf/fyrom05.html RSSSF.com]\n\n<!--Update team positions here-->\n|team1=RAB |team2=VAR |team3=POB |team4=SIL |team5=SHK |team6=BAS |team7=BRE |team8=BEL |team9=CEM |team10=MAD |team11=SLO |team12=NAP\n\n<!--Update team qualifications here (defined below)-->\n|result1=CL1Q |result2=UC1Q |result3=IC1 |result4=IC1 |result6=UC1CQ |result9=RPO |result10=RPO |result11=REL |result12=REL\n\n<!--Update team results here and then (if needed positions above). Don't forget to update the date (update parameter)-->\n|update=complete\n|win_BAS=14|draw_BAS=7 |loss_BAS=12|gf_BAS=53|ga_BAS=47<!-- Bashkimi -->\n|win_BEL=14|draw_BEL=6 |loss_BEL=13|gf_BEL=37|ga_BEL=32<!-- Belasica -->\n|win_BRE=14|draw_BRE=6 |loss_BRE=13|gf_BRE=55|ga_BRE=60<!-- Bregalnica Kraun -->\n|win_CEM=13|draw_CEM=7 |loss_CEM=13|gf_CEM=54|ga_CEM=50<!-- Cementarnica 55 -->\n|win_MAD=12|draw_MAD=5 |loss_MAD=16|gf_MAD=44|ga_MAD=55<!-- Madjari Solidarnost -->\n|win_NAP=1 |draw_NAP=4 |loss_NAP=28|gf_NAP=17|ga_NAP=99<!-- Napredok -->\n|win_POB=16|draw_POB=7 |loss_POB=10|gf_POB=59|ga_POB=49<!-- Pobeda -->\n|win_RAB=25|draw_RAB=3 |loss_RAB=5 |gf_RAB=66|ga_RAB=23<!-- Rabotnichki Kometal -->\n|win_SHK=15|draw_SHK=5 |loss_SHK=13|gf_SHK=59|ga_SHK=40<!-- Shk\u00ebndija -->\n|win_SIL=15|draw_SIL=6 |loss_SIL=12|gf_SIL=56|ga_SIL=37<!-- Sileks -->\n|win_SLO=5 |draw_SLO=2 |loss_SLO=26|gf_SLO=37|ga_SLO=80<!-- Sloga Jugomagnat 