ar Stojanovski]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[FK Belasica|Belasica]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|26\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Macedonia}} [[Stevica Risti\u0107]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[FK Sileks|Sileks]]\n|-\n|3\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Brazil}} [[Wandeir Oliveira dos Santos|Wandeir]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[FK Vardar|Vardar]]\n|19\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|4\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Macedonia}} [[Blazhe Ilijoski]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[FK Rabotni\u010dki|Rabotnichki]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|17\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Macedonia}} [[Riste Naumov]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[FK Vardar|Vardar]]\n|-\n|6\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Macedonia}} [[Zoran Miserdovski]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[KF Bashkimi (1947\u20132008)|Bashkimi]]\n|14\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|7\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Macedonia}} [[Ismail Ismaili]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[KF Shk\u00ebndija|Shk\u00ebndija]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|12\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Macedonia}} [[Aleksandar Toleski]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[FK Cementarnica 55|Cementarnica]]\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagicon|Macedonia}} [[Nikol\u010de Zdravevski|Nikolche Zdravevski]]\n|align=\"left\"|[[FK Pobeda|Pobeda]]\n|-\n|}\n\n<small>Source: [http://www.rsssf.com/tablesf/fyrom05.html rsssf.com]</small>\n\n==See also==\n*[[2004\u201305 Macedonian Football Cup]]\n*[[2004\u201305 Macedonian Second Football League]]\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesf/fyrom05.html Macedonia - List of final tables (RSSSF)]\n*[http://ffm.mk/ Football Federation of Macedonia]\n\n{{Macedonian First Football League}}\n{{2004\u201305 in Republic of Macedonia football}}\n{{2004\u201305 in European Football (UEFA)}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2004-05 First Macedonian Football League}}\n[[Category:2004\u201305 in European association football leagues|Macedonia]]\n[[Category:2004\u201305 in Republic of Macedonia football|1]]\n[[Category:Macedonian First Football League seasons]]\n", "name_user": "Jolicnikola", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eLeague table", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2004%E2%80%9305_Ma